line 209=>"Gandalf for certain this time," he thought as he puffed along the passage. But 
line 210=>it was not. It was two more dwarves, both with blue hoods, silver belts, and yellow 
line 211=>beards;  and  each  of  them  carried  a  bag  of  tools  and  a  spade.  In  they  hopped,  as 
