line 463=>"Excitable  little  fellow,"  said  Gandalf,  as  they  sat  down  again.  "Gets  funny 
line 464=>queer  fits,  but  he  is  one  of  the  best,  one  of  the  best-as  fierce  as  a  dragon  in  a 
line 465=>pinch." 
line 466=>If  you  have  ever  seen  a  dragon  in  a  pinch,  you will  realize  that  this was  only 
line 467=>poetical  exaggeration  applied  to  any  hobbit,  even  to Old Took's  great-granduncle 
