line 2062=>but  he  did  not  feel  at  all  sure  how  the  game  was  going  to  end,  whether  Gollum 
line 2063=>guessed right or not. 
line 2064=>"Time's up!" he said. 
line 2065=>"String,  or  nothing!"  shrieked  Gollum,  which  was  not  quite  fair-working  in 
