line 2095=>endless dark days. "That's what we wants now, yes; we wants it!" 
line 2096=>
line 2097=>####-He  wanted  it  because  it  was  a  ring  of  power,  and  if  you  slipped  that  ring on 
line 2098=>your  finger,  you  were  invisible;  only  in  the  full  sunlight  could  you  be  seen,  and 
line 2099=>then only by your shadow, and that would be shaky and faint. 
line 2100=>"My  birthday-present! It came to me on my birthday, my precious," So he had 
line 2101=>always  said  to  himself.  But  who  knows  how Gollum  came  by  that  present,  ages 
