line 2404=>"And  here's  the  burglar!"  said  Bilbo  stepping  down  into  the  middle  of  them, 
line 2405=>and slipping off the ring. 
line 2406=>Bless  me,  how  they  jumped!  Then  they  shouted  with  surprise  and  delight. 
line 2407=>Gandalf was as astonished as any of  them, but probably more pleased than all the 
line 2408=>others. He called to Balin and told him what he thought of a look-out man who let 
