line 2413=>very clever bit of work. 
line 2414=>Indeed Bilbo was  so  pleased with  their  praise  that he just chuckled inside and 
line 2415=>said nothing whatever about  the  ring; and when  they asked him how he did  it, he 
line 2416=>said: "O, just crept along, you know-very carefully and quietly." 
line 2417=>
