line 2437=>"But I squeezed through all right-and here I am." 
line 2438=>The  dwarves  looked  at  him  with  quite  a  new  respect,  when  he  talked  about 
line 2439=>dodging  guards,  jumping  over  Gollum,  and  squeezing  through,  as  if  it  was  not 
