line 2441=>"What  did  I  tell  you?"  said  Gandalf  laughing.  "Mr.  Baggins  has more  about 
line 2442=>him than you guess." He gave Bilbo a queer look from under his bushy eyebrows, 
line 2443=>as he said this, and the hobbit wondered if he guessed at the part of his tale that he 
line 2444=>had left out. 
line 2445=>Then he had questions of his own to ask, for if Gandalf had explained it all by 
line 2446=>now  to  the  dwarves,  Bilbo  had  not  heard  it.  He  wanted  to  know  how  the  wizard 
