line 2492=>
line 2493=>####-"I  am  so dreadfully hungry," groaned Bilbo, who was  suddenly  aware  that he 
line 2494=>had  not  had  a meal  since  the  night  before  the  night  before  last.  Just  think  of  that 
line 2495=>for  a  hobbit!  His  stomach  felt  all  empty  and  loose  and  his  legs  all  wobbly,  now 
