line 2710=>eyes shining as red and fierce as the flames. 
line 2711=>Then  suddenly  goblins  came  running  up  yelling.  They  thought  a  battle  with 
line 2712=>the  woodmen  was  going  on;  but  they  goon  learned  what  had  really  happened. 
