line 3421=>drink. There is one stream there, I know, black and strong which crosses the path. 
line 3422=>That  you  should  neither  drink  of,  nor  bathe  in;  for  I  have  heard  that  it  carries 
line 3423=>enchantment and a great drowsiness and forgetfulness. And in the dim shadows of 
