line 3865=>singing, and I could not count or describe the things there were to eat and drink." 
line 3866=>"You need not try," said Thorin. "In fact if you can't talk about something else, 
line 3867=>you  had  better  be  silent.  We  are  quite  annoyed  enough  with  you  as  it  is.  If  you 
