line 3903=>After  a  good  deal  of  creeping  and  crawling  they  peered  round  the  trunks  and 
line 3904=>looked  into  a  clearing where  some  trees  had  been  felled  and  the  ground  levelled. 
line 3905=>There were many people there, elvish-looking folk, all dressed in green and brown 
