line 4022=>cries for help had come in the night â€“ and by luck (he was born with a good share 
line 4023=>of  it) be guessed more or  less  right, as you will  see. Having made up his mind he 
line 4024=>crept  along  as  cleverly  as  he  could.  Hobbits  are  clever  at quietness,  especially  in 
