line 4036=>he could make out many of  the words  that  they said. They were  talking about  the 
line 4037=>dwarves! 
line 4038=>"It was  a  sharp  struggle, but worth  it,"  said one.  "What nasty  thick  skins  they 
line 4039=>have to be sure, but I'll wager there is good juice inside." 
line 4040=>
line 4041=>####-"Aye, they'll make fine eating, when they've hung a bit," said another.  
line 4042=>"Don't  hang  'em  too  long,"  said  a  third.  "They're  not  as  fat  as  they might  be. 
line 4043=>Been feeding none too well of late, I should guess." 
