line 4242=>backwards  and  forwards,  slashing  at  spider-threads,  hacking  at  their  legs,  and 
line 4243=>stabbing  at  their  fat  bodies  if  they  came  too  near.  The  spiders  swelled  with  rage, 
line 4244=>and  spluttered  and  frothed,  and  hissed  out  horrible  curses;  but  they  had  become 
