line 4253=>the spiders did not like. At any rate here the light was greener, and the boughs less 
line 4254=>thick and threatening, and they had a chance to rest and draw breath. 
line 4255=>There they lay for some time, puffing and panting. put very soon they began to 
line 4256=>ask questions. They had to have the whole vanishing business carefully explained, 
