line 5708=>"You  don't  know  everything, O  Smaug  the Mighty,"  said  he.  "Not  gold  alone 
line 5709=>brought us hither." 
line 5710=>
line 5711=>####-"Ha! Ha! You  admit  the  'us',"  laughed Smaug. "Why not say  'us fourteen' and 
line 5712=>be  done  with  it.  Mr.  Lucky  Number?  I  am  pleased  to  hear  that  you  had  other 
