line 5882=>it shone like silver in the firelight, like water in the sun, like snow under the stars, 
line 5883=>like rain upon the Moon!" 
line 5884=>But  the enchanted desire of  the hoard had  fallen  from Bilbo. All  through  their 
line 5885=>talk  he  was  only  half  listening  to  them.  He  sat  nearest  to  the  door with  one  ear 
