line 6545=>on: 
line 6546=>"So  much  for  joy,  Thorin  Oakenshield.  You  may  go  back  to  your  halls  in 
line 6547=>safety;  all  the  treasure  is  yours-for  the  moment.  But  many  are  gathering  hither 
line 6548=>beside  the  birds.  The  news  of  the  death  of  the  guardian  has  already  gone  far  and 
