line 6563=>Then Thorin burst forth in anger: "Our thanks, RÃ³ac Carc's son. You and your 
line 6564=>people shall not be forgotten. But none of our gold shall thieves take or the violent 
line 6565=>carry  off  while  we  are  alive.  If  you  would  earn  our  thanks  still  more,  bring  us 
