line 6880=>make you an offer!!" 
line 6881=>"Let us hear it!" they said. 
line 6882=>"You may  see  it!"  said  he.  "It  is  this!"  and  he  drew  forth  the Arkenstone,  and 
line 6883=>threw away the wrapping. 
line 6884=>The Elvenking himself, whose eyes were used to things of wonder and beauty, 
