line 6886=>globe had been  filled with moonlight and hung before  them  in a net woven of  the 
line 6887=>glint of frosty stars. 
line 6888=>"This  is  the  Arkenstone  of  Thrain,"  said  Bilbo,  "the  Heart  of  the  Mountain; 
line 6889=>and  it  is  also  the  heart  of  Thorin.  He  values  it  above  a  river  of  gold.  I  give  it  to 
