line 9048=>     As for Bilbo Baggins,  even while he was making his speech, he had been 
line 9049=>fingering the golden ring   in his pocket:  his magic ring that he  had  kept 
line 9050=>secret for so many years. As he  stepped  down he slipped it on his  finger, 
line 9051=>and he was never seen by any hobbit in Hobbiton again. 
line 9052=>     He walked  briskly back to his hole, and stood  for a moment  listening 
