line 9071=>     'Hullo!' said Bilbo. 'I wondered if you would turn up.' 
line 9072=>     'I am glad to find you visible,' replied the wizard, sitting down  in a  
line 9073=>chair, 'I wanted to catch you and have a few final words. I suppose you feel 
line 9074=>that everything has gone off splendidly and according to plan?' 
line 9075=>     'Yes,  I do,' said  Bilbo. "Though that flash was surprising: it  quite 
