line 9237=>     Now far ahead the Road has gone, 
line 9238=>     And I must follow, if I can, 
line 9239=>     Pursuing it with eager feet, 
line 9240=>     Until it joins some larger way 
line 9241=>     Where many paths and errands meet. 
