line 11233=>more of me! But my heart forbodes that, ere all is ended, you,  Frodo son of 
line 11234=>Drogo, will  know more  of  these  fell things than  Gildor  Inglorion.  May 
line 11235=>Elbereth protect you!' 
line 11236=>     'But where shall I find courage?' asked Frodo. 'That is what I  chiefly 
