line 12072=>can trust us to keep any secret of yours  - closer than you keep it yourself.  
line 12073=>But you cannot trust us to let you face trouble alone, and go off  without a  
line 12074=>word. We  are your friends, Frodo. Anyway: there it is. We know most of what 
line 12075=>Gandalf has  told you. We know  a good deal about the Ring. We  are horribly 
