line 12530=>receive them as the  tree swayed and creaked. They looked up at the grey and 
line 12531=>yellow leaves, moving softly against the light, and singing. They shut their 
line 12532=>eyes, and  then it seemed  that  they  could almost hear words,  cool words,  
line 12533=>saying something about water and sleep. They gave themselves up to the spell 
