line 12802=>
line 12803=>####-me. 
line 12804=>     O slender as a willow-wand! O clearer than clear water! 
line 12805=>     O reed by the living pool! Fair River-daughter! 
line 12806=>     O spring-time and summer-time, and spring again after! 
line 12807=>     O wind on the waterfall, and the leaves' laughter!'  
