line 13535=>     Old Tom Bombadil is a merry fellow,  
line 13536=>     Bright blue his jacket is, and his boots are yellow.  
line 13537=>     None has ever caught him yet, for Tom, he is the master: 
line 13538=>
line 13539=>####-     His songs are stronger songs, and his feet are faster. 
line 13540=>     There was a loud rumbling sound, as of stones rolling and  falling, and 
