line 13756=>     'No, I hope not  tonight,' answered Tom Bombadil; 'nor perhaps the next 
line 13757=>day. But do not trust my guess; for I  cannot tell  for certain. Out east my 
line 13758=>knowledge fails. Tom is not master of  Riders from the Black Land far beyond 
