line 13799=>     Before  them rose Bree-hill barring the way,  a dark mass against misty 
line 13800=>stars; and under  its western flank nestled a large village. Towards it they 
line 13801=>now  hurried desiring only to find a fire,  and a door  between them and the 
line 13802=>night. 
