line 14043=>forget that you are supposed to be  escaping in secret, and are still on the 
line 14044=>high-road and not very far from the Shire!' 
line 14045=>     'All right!' said Pippin. 'Mind yourself!  Don't  get  lost,  and don't  
line 14046=>forget that it is safer indoors!' 
line 14047=>     The company  was in the big common-room  of the inn.  The gathering was 
line 14048=>large  and mixed, as Frodo discovered, when his eyes got used  to the light. 
line 14049=>This came chiefly from a blazing  log-fire, for the three lamps hanging from 
