line 14098=>prospect. 
line 14099=>     The hobbits  did not pay much attention to all this,  and it did not at 
line 14100=>the moment seem to concern hobbits. Big  Folk could hardly  beg for lodgings 
line 14101=>in hobbit-holes. They were more  interested in Sam and Pippin,  who were now 
