line 14110=>
line 14111=>####-     Suddenly  Frodo  noticed  that  a  strange-looking  weather -beaten man, 
line 14112=>sitting in  the  shadows near the  wall, was  also listening intently to the 
line 14113=>hobbit-talk. He had  a  tall tankard  in  front of him, and  was  smoking  a  
