line 15209=>make for the line of hills, not for Weathertop. There we can strike a path I 
line 15210=>know that runs at their feet; it will  bring us to Weathertop from the north 
line 15211=>and less openly. Then we shall see what we shall see.' 
line 15212=>     All that day they plodded along, until the cold  and early evening came 
