line 16963=>ill 
line 16964=>(if people were ever ill in Rivendell), and had been unable  to  come to the 
line 16965=>feast. His head seemed sunk  in sleep on  his breast, and a fold of his dark 
line 16966=>cloak was drawn over his face. 
