line 17679=>Sword of Elendil that broke beneath him when  he fell. It has been treasured 
line 17680=>by  his  heirs when all other heirlooms  were lost; for it was spoken of old 
line 17681=>among  us that it should be made  again when the  Ring, Isildur's  Bane, was 
line 17682=>found. Now you have seen the sword that you have sought, what would you 
line 17683=>ask? 
