line 18893=>     He took from the box  a small sword in an old shabby leathern scabbard.  
line 18894=>Then he drew it, and  its polished and well -tended blade glittered suddenly, 
line 18895=>
line 18896=>####-cold  and bright. 'This is Sting,' he said, and thrust it with little effort 
