line 19339=>     Laboriously they climbed a  sharp slope and halted for a  moment at the 
line 19340=>top. Frodo felt a soft touch on his face. He put out his arm and saw the dim 
line 19341=>white flakes of snow settling on his sleeve. 
line 19342=>     They went on. But before  long the snow was falling fast,  filling  all 
