line 19379=>wild  howls  of  laughter.  Stones  began  to  fall  from the mountain-side, 
line 19380=>whistling over  their heads, or crashing on the path beside them. Every  now 
line 19381=>and  again they heard a dull  rumble,  as a gr eat  boulder rolled  down from 
