line 20021=>of  ithildin  that mirrors only starlight  and moonlight, and sleeps until it 
line 20022=>is touched by one who speaks words now long forgotten in Middle-earth. It is 
line 20023=>long since I heard them, and I thought deeply  before I could recall them to 
line 20024=>my mind.' 
line 20025=>     'What does the writing  say?' asked  Frodo, who was trying  to decipher  
