line 20096=>     'Do not let him run away! ' said Boromir. 'It seems that we  shall need 
line 20097=>him still, if the wolves do not  find us. How  I  hate  this foul pool! ' He 
line 20098=>stooped and picking up a large stone he cast it far into the dark water. 
line 20099=>     The stone vanished with a soft slap; but at  the same instant there was 
line 20100=>a swish and a bubble. Great rippling rings formed on the surface  out beyond  
