line 20112=>     With a suddenness that startled them all the wizard sprang to his feet. 
line 20113=>He was laughing! `I have it! '  he  cried. 'Of  course, of  course! Absurdly 
line 20114=>simple, like most riddles when you see the answer.' 
line 20115=>     Picking up  his  staff he  stood before  the rock and  said  in  a clear 
line 20116=>voice: Mellon! 
line 20117=>     The  star  shone  out briefly  and faded again.  Then silently  a great 
