line 20199=>should not be touched. We  may  not  have a chance of filling  our skins and 
line 20200=>bottles till we come down into Dimrill Dale.' 
line 20201=>     'How long is that going to take us? ' asked Frodo. 
line 20202=>     'I  cannot  say,'  answered Gandalf.  'It depends  on many chances. But 
line 20203=>going straight,  without mishap  or  losing our  way, we shall take three or  
line 20204=>
