line 21076=>     They rose and looked about  them. Northward the dale ran up into a glen  
line 21077=>of shadows between  two great arms of the mountains, above which three white 
line 21078=>peaks were shining:  Celebdil, Fanuidhol, Caradhras. the Mountains of Moria. 
line 21079=>At the head of  the glen a torrent flowed  like a white lace over an endless 
line 21080=>ladder  of short  falls,  and  a   mist of foam  hung in the  air  about  the 
