line 21475=>     Out of  the  shadows a  ladder  was  let  down:  it  was made  of rope, 
line 21476=>silver -grey and  glimmering  in the dark, and  though it looked  slender  it 
line 21477=>proved  strong enough to bear  many men. Legolas ran  lightly up, and  Frodo 
line 21478=>followed slowly; behind  came Sam trying not to breathe loudly. The branches 
line 21479=>of the mallorn-tree grew  out nearly straight from the trunk, and then swept 
