line 21481=>
line 21482=>####-and  among these they  found that there had been built a wooden platform, or 
line 21483=>flet as such things were called in those days: the  Elves called it a talan. 
line 21484=>It  was  reached  by a round hole in  the  centre  through  which the ladder  
line 21485=>passed. 
line 21486=>     When Frodo came at last up on to the flet he found Legolas seated  with 
