line 21554=>     `Once I do get to sleep,' said Sam, 'i  shall go on sleeping, whether I 
line 21555=>roll off or no. And the less said,  the sooner I'll drop off, if you take my 
line 21556=>meaning.' 
line 21557=>
line 21558=>####-     Frodo  lay  for some  time awake,  and looked up  at the stars glinting 
