line 21566=>     Late in the  night he awoke. The  other hobbits were  asleep. The Elves 
line 21567=>were gone. The sickle Moon was gleaming dimly among the leaves. The wind 
line 21568=>was 
line 21569=>still. A little way off he heard a harsh laugh and the tread of many feet on 
