line 21646=>     `No!' said Haldir. `We have two  more ropes. We  will fasten them above 
line 21647=>the other, one shoulder-high,  and another half-high, and holding these  the 
line 21648=>strangers should be able to cross with care.' 
line 21649=>     When this  slender bridge had been made, the Company passed  over, some 
