line 21701=>     `Now let us cry: "a plague on the stiff necks of Elves!"' said Aragorn. 
line 21702=>`But the Company shall all fare alike. Come, bind our eyes Haldir! ' 
line 21703=>     `I shall claim  full amends for every fall and  stubbed  toe, if you do 
