line 23379=>     `I can't abide fog,' said  Sam; `but this  seems to be a lucky one. Now 
line 23380=>perhaps we can get away without those cursed goblins seeing us.' 
line 23381=>     `Perhaps so,'  said Aragorn. `But it  will  be  hard to find  the  path 
