line 23445=>     `That would not be easy, even if we were all Men,' said Boromir. 
line 23446=>     `Yet such as we are we will try it,' said Aragorn. 
line 23447=>     'Aye, we  will,' said Gimli. `The legs of Men will lag on a rough road, 
