line 23660=>     Wandering  aimlessly at first in the  wood, Frodo found  that his  feet 
line 23661=>
line 23662=>####-were leading  him up towards the  slopes of the hill. He came to a path, the 
line 23663=>dwindling ruins of a  road of long  ago. In steep places stairs of stone had 
