line 23692=>     Suddenly Boromir came and sat beside him. `Are you sure that you do not 
line 23693=>suffer needlessly? ' he said. `I wish to help you. You need counsel in  your 
line 23694=>hard choice. Will you not take mine? ' 
line 23695=>     'I  think I know already  what counsel you would  give, Boromir,'  said 
line 23696=>Frodo. 'And it would seem like wisdom but for the warning of my heart.' 
