line 24107=>bring them over  the grey hills of the Emyn Muil, and  down into the Land of 
line 24108=>Shadow. 
line 24109=>  
line 24110=>
line 24111=>####-     
line 24112=>Here ends the first part of the history of the War of the Ring. 
line 24113=>     The second part is called THE TWO TOWERS, since the events recounted 
line 24114=>in it are dominated by ORTHANC,  the citadel  of  Saruman, and  the fortress 
line 24115=>of MINAS MORGUL  that guards the secret entrance  to Mordor;  it  tells  of 
line 24116=>the deeds and  perils of  all  the members of the now sundered fellowship, until 
line 24117=>the coming of the Great Darkness. 
line 24118=>     The  third part tells of the  last defence against the Shadow,  and the 
line 24119=>end of the mission of the Ring-bearer in  THE RETURN OF THE KING. 
