line 25990=>     'You seem to  have been doing well, Master Took,' said Merry.  'You will 
line 25991=>get  almost  a chapter in old Bilbo's book, if ever I get a chance to report 
line 25992=>to him. Good work: especially guessing that hairy villain's little game, and 
