line 26606=>     After some time the hobbits heard him murmuring  again. He seemed to be 
line 26607=>counting  on his fingers. 'Fangorn,  Finglas, Fladrif, aye, aye,' he sighed. 
line 26608=>'The trouble is  that there are so  few of us left,' he said turning towards 
line 26609=>the hobbits. 'Only  three remain of the first Ents that walked in the  woods 
