line 26690=>Entwives are only a memory for us, and our  beards  are  long and  grey. The 
line 26691=>Elves made many songs concerning the Search of  the  Ents,  and some of  the 
line 26692=>
line 26693=>####-songs passed into the tongues of  Men. But we made  no songs about it, being 
