line 26778=>it was earthier and  richer, more sustaining and  food-like,  so  to  speak. 
line 26779=>While the hobbits drank, sitting on the edge of  the bed, and nibbling small 
line 26780=>pieces of elf-cake (more because they felt that eating was a  necessary part 
