line 27080=>     'But Saruman will try to stop you. won't he?' 
line 27081=>     'Hm,  ah, yes, that is so. I  have  not  forgotten  it.  Indeed  I have 
line 27082=>thought long about it. But. you see, many of the Ents are younger than I am.  
