line 27501=>mighty  one  may suddenly  appear, wielding the Ring, and assailing him with 
line 27502=>war, seeking to cast him  down and take his  place. That we  should wish  to 
line 27503=>cast him down and have no one in his place is not a thought that  occurs  to 
line 27504=>his  mind. That we should try to destroy the Ring itself has not yet entered 
