line 27509=>enough, may need  to strike no  more.  So the forces that he has  long  been 
line 27510=>preparing he is now  setting in motion, sooner than he intended.  Wise  fool. 
line 27511=>For if he had used all his power to guard Mordor,  so that none could enter, 
line 27512=>and bent  all his guild  to the hunting of the  Ring, then indeed hope would 
line 27513=>have faded: neither  Ring nor Bearer could long have eluded him. But now his 
