line 28508=>even when his heart grew colder, he found you useful still. But for long now 
line 28509=>he  has plotted  your  ruin, wearing the  mask of Friendship,  until  he was 
line 28510=>ready. In those years Wormtongue's task was easy, and all that  you did  was 
line 28511=>swiftly known in Isengard; for your  land  was  open, and strangers came and 
line 28512=>
