line 28770=>     'Maybe you will wait long,' said the other. 
line 28771=>     The host turned away now from  the  road to the  Fords of Isen and bent 
line 28772=>their course southward. Night fell,  a nd still they rode on. The hills  drew 
line 28773=>near, but the tall peaks of Thrihyrne were already dim against the darkening 
