line 28844=>     'It is a great host and follows us hard,' said Aragorn. 
line 28845=>     'They br ing fire,' said Thjoden,  'and they are  burning as  they come, 
line 28846=>rick, cot, and tree. This was  a rich vale and had many homesteads. Alas for  
line 28847=>my folk!' 
line 28848=>     'Would that day  was here and we might ride down upon them like a storm 
