line 29429=>     The Men of the Mark took their weapons from them, and set them to work. 
line 29430=>     'Help  now  to  repa ir  the  evil  in  which  you  have  joined,'  said 
line 29431=>Erkenbrand;  'and afterwards you  shall take an oath never again to pass the 
