line 30290=>walls. But arrows are no  use against Ents. They hurt  them, of  course, and 
line 30291=>infuriate them:  like stinging flies. But an  Ent  can  be  stuck as full of 
line 30292=>orc-arrows  as  a pin -cushion,  and take no serious  harm.  They  cannot  be 
line 30293=>poisoned,  for one thing; and their skin seems to be very thick, and tougher  
