line 30643=>     They passed through the ruined tunnel and stood upon a heap of  stones, 
line 30644=>gazing at the  dark rock of Orthanc, and its many windows, a menace still in 
line 30645=>the  desolation  that  lay  all about  it.  The waters  had  now  nearly all 
line 30646=>subsided.  Here  and  there  gloomy pools  remained,  covered with  scum and 
line 30647=>wreckage; but most of the wide circle was bare again, a  wilderness of slime 
