line 30652=>ravine  between the  dark arms  of  the mountains. Across the waste they saw 
line 30653=>riders picking their way; they were coming from the north  side, and already 
line 30654=>they were drawing near to Orthanc. 
line 30655=>     'There is  Gandalf, and Thjoden and his men!' said Legolas. 'Let  us go 
