line 31609=>let Rohan look to its horses!  
line 31610=>
line 31611=>####-     'But I cannot tell how it will fall out, well or ill for us. It may  be 
line 31612=>that the counsels of the Enemy will  be confused,  or hindered by  his wrath 
line 31613=>with Saruman. It  may be that he will learn that  I was there and stood upon 
