line 31791=>grunted. `Well, I  suppose it's always easier getting down than up. Those as 
line 31792=>can't fly can jump!' 
line 31793=>     `It would be a big jump still,' said Frodo. `About, well'  --  he  stood 
line 31794=>for a moment measuring it with his eyes  -- `about eighteen  fathoms I should  
