line 31928=>     `Ah! Who would? ' said Sam. `Elves are wonderful folk. It looks  a  bit 
line 31929=>thin, but it's tough; and soft as milk to the  hand. Packs close too, and as 
line 31930=>light as light. Wonderful folk to be sure!' 
line 31931=>     `Thirty ells! '  said Frodo considering. 'I believe it would be enough. 
line 31932=>If the storm passes before nightfall, I'm going to try it.' 
line 31933=>     `The rain's nearly  given over already,'  said Sam;  'but  don't you go 
