line 32812=>trying to encourage him with clumsy words.  
line 32813=>     When day came at last the hobbits were surprised to see how much closer 
line 32814=>the ominous mountains had already drawn. The air was now clearer and colder, 
line 32815=>and though still far off, the walls of Mordor were no longer a cloudy menace 
