line 32859=>ash-heaps of the Dark Lord. 
line 32860=>     Too weary  to go  further  they sought for some place where they  could 
line 32861=>rest. For a while  they sat without speaking  under the shadow of a mound of 
line 32862=>slag; but foul fumes  leaked out of it, catching their  throats and  choking 
