line 32937=>call  of the Ring. The Dark Lord was He, of course; but Sam wondered who 
line 32938=>She 
line 32939=>was. One of  the nasty friends the little wretch had made in his wanderings, 
line 32940=>he supposed.  Then he  forgot the  point, for things had  plainly  gone  far 
line 32941=>enough, and were getting dangerous. A great heaviness  was in all his limbs,  
