line 33158=>passed away. These were Men  of  other  race, out  of  the  wide  Eastlands, 
line 33159=>gathering  to the summons of their Overlord; armies that had encamped before 
line 33160=>his  Gate by  night  and  now marched in to swell  his mounting power. As if 
