line 33163=>frail grey hood close upon his head, and stepped down into the dell. Then he 
line 33164=>turned to Gollum. 
line 33165=>     `Smjagol,' he said, `I will trust you once more. lndeed it seems that I 
line 33166=>must do so,  and that it is my fate to receive help from you. where  I least  
line 33167=>looked  for  it, and  your  fate to help me whom you long  pursued with evil 
