line 33171=>tried to take  from  me what you once sought.  May the third time  prove the 
line 33172=>best! But I warn you, Smjagol, you are in danger.' 
line 33173=>     `Yes, yes,  master!  '  said Gollum. `Dreadful  danger! Smjagol's bones 
line 33174=>shake to think of it. but he doesn't run away. He must help nice master.' 
line 33175=>     'I  did not mean  the danger that we all  share,' said Frodo. 'I mean a  
line 33176=>danger to yourself alone. You swore a promise by what you call the Precious.  
line 33177=>Remember tha t! It will hold you to it; but it will seek a way to twist it to 
line 33178=>your own undoing. Already you are being twisted. You revealed yourself to me 
line 33179=>just  now, foolishly.  Give it back  to  Smjagol you  said. Do  not say that 
