line 33486=>     For the few hours of daylight that were left they rested, shifting into 
line 33487=>the shade as the sun moved, until  at last the shadow of the western  rim of 
line 33488=>their  dell grew long, and darkness filled all  the hollow. Then they ate  a  
line 33489=>little,  and drank  sparingly.  Gollum  ate nothing, but  he  accepted water  
