line 33491=>     `Soon get more now,' he said, licking  his lips. `Good water  runs down 
line 33492=>in  streams to  the Great River,  nice water in the lands  we are  going to. 
line 33493=>Smjagol will get food there too, perhaps. He's very hungry, yes, gollum! ' He 
