line 33601=>suddenly Sam laughed, for heart's ease not for jest. They followed a  stream 
line 33602=>that went  quickly down before them. Presently  it  brought them to a  small 
line 33603=>clear lake in a shallow dell: it lay in the broken ruins of an ancient stone 
line 33604=>basin, the carven rim of  which was  almost wholly  covered  with mosses and 
