line 34094=>Isildur, so far as old tales tell. But orc-arrows are plenty,  and the sight 
line 34095=>of one would not be taken as a  sign of Doom by Boromir of  Gondor.  Had you  
line 34096=>this thing  in keeping?  It is hidden, you say;  but is not that because you  
