line 34565=>glazed brown clay or turned box-wood, smooth and clean. Here and there was a  
line 34566=>cup or basin of polished bronze; and a goblet of plain  silver was set by the 
line 34567=>Captain's seat in the middle of the inmost table. 
line 34568=>     Faramir went about  among the men, questioning each as he came in, in a  
