line 35042=>     'Fissh, nice fissh. White Face has vanished, my precious, at last, yes.  
line 35043=>Now we can eat fish in  peace. No, not in peace,  precious. For Precious  is 
line 35044=>lost; yes, lost. Dirty hobbits, nasty hobbits. Gone and left us, gollum; and 
