line 35526=>became  more frequent  as they  got nearer the  top; very old and  tall they 
line 35527=>were, gaunt and leggy below but thick above, and already  putting out yellow 
line 35528=>flowers  that  glimmered in the gloom and gave a faint  sweet scent. So tall 
