line 35593=>     `You forget the Marshes,' said Frodo.  `I hope nothing has happened  to 
line 35594=>him.' 
line 35595=>     `And I hope he's  up to  no  tricks. And anyway I  hope he doesn't fall 
line 35596=>into other hands, as you might say. Because if he does, we  shall soon be in 
line 35597=>for trouble.' 
line 35598=>     At that moment a rolling and rumbling noise was heard again, louder now 
