line 36371=>in  a  little  picture drawn  by  elven-fingers  he  saw  the Lady Galadriel 
line 36372=>standing on the  grass  in  Lurien,  and gifts  were  in her hands. And you, 
line 36373=>Ring-bearer, he  heard her say,  remote  but clear, for you  I have prepared  
line 36374=>this. 
line 36375=>     The bubbling hiss  drew nearer,  and there  was a  creaking as  of some 
line 36376=>great jointed thing that moved with slow purpose in the dark. A reek came on 
line 36377=>before it. 'Master, master!' cried Sam, and the  life and  urgency came back  
