line 36854=>The errand must not fail.' 
line 36855=>     `I wish I wasn't the last,' he groaned. `I wish old Gandalf was hare or  
line 36856=>somebody. Why am I left all alone to make up my mind?  I'm sure to go wrong. 
line 36857=>And it's not for me to go taking the Ring, putting myself forward.' 
line 36858=>     'But you haven't put yourself forward; you've been  put forward. And as 
