line 36882=>I would wish to come back and find you again. Good-bye!  ' 
line 36883=>     And then he bent his own  neck and put the chain upon  it, and  at once 
line 36884=>his head was bowed to the ground with the weight of  the Ring, as if a great 
line 36885=>stone  had been strung on him. But slowly, as if the weight became  less, or  
