line 36894=>     He  had not far to go.  The  tunnel was some way  behind;  the  Cleft a  
line 36895=>couple of hundred yards ahead, or less. The path was visible in  the dusk` a  
line 36896=>deep rut worn in  ages of  passage,  running  now gently up in a long trough 
line 36897=>with cliffs on either side. The trough narrowed rapidly. Soon Sam came  to a  
line 36898=>
line 36899=>####-long flight of broad shallow steps. Now the orc-tower  was right  above him, 
line 36900=>frowning black, and in it the red eye  glowed. Now he was hidden in the dark 
line 36901=>shadow under it. He was coming to the top of  the steps and was in the Cleft  
