line 36903=>     'I've made up  my  mind,' he kept saying to himself.  But  he  had not. 
line 36904=>Though  he  had done his best  to  think it  out,  what  he  was  doing  was 
line 36905=>altogether against the grain  of his nature.  `Have  I  got it  wrong? '  he 
