line 37581=>     'Kingship?' said Pippin amazed. 
line 37582=>     'Yes,' said  Gandalf.  'If you  have  walked all these days with closed 
line 37583=>ears and mind asleep, wake up now!' He knocked on the door. 
line 37584=>     The door opened,  but no one could be  seen  to open it.  Pippin looked 
