line 37929=>
line 37930=>####-     Shadowfax  whinnied as Pippin  entered the stable and  turned his head. 
line 37931=>'Good morning!'  said Pippin.  'Gandalf will come  as soon as  he may. He is 
line 37932=>busy, but he sends greetings, and I am to see that all is well with you; and 
