line 37961=>could look out on the morning over the world. 
line 37962=>     They  ate  and drank; and they  talked now of  Gondor and its  ways and 
line 37963=>customs, now  of the Shire and the strange countries that  Pippin  had seen. 
line 37964=>And ever as they talked Beregond  was more amazed,  and looked with  greater  
