line 38046=>slowed up again.' 
line 38047=>     'Only because  everything is now ready,' said Beregond. 'It  is but the 
line 38048=>deep breath before the plunge.' 
line 38049=>     'But why were the beacons lit last night?' 
line 38050=>     'It is  over-late  to  send  for aid  when you  are  already besieged,' 
