line 38279=>what 
line 38280=>are they? We hoped for ten times the number. That will be the new tidings of 
line 38281=>the  black fleet.  They  are sparing only a tithe  of  their strength. Still 
line 38282=>every little is a gain.' 
line 38283=>     And  so  the  companies  came and  were hailed and  cheered  and passed 
line 38284=>through  the Gate, men of the Outlands marching to defend the City of Gondor  
