line 38341=>     The lodging was   dark,  save  for a  little lantern  set  on the table. 
line 38342=>Gandalf was  not there.  Gloom settled  still  more  heavily  on Pippin.  He 
line 38343=>climbed on the bench  and tried  to  peer out of a window,  but it was  like 
