line 38459=>     'Always my days  have seemed  to me  too short to  achieve  my desire,' 
line 38460=>answered Aragorn. 'But great indeed will be my haste ere I take that road.' 
line 38461=>     'That  will soon  be seen,' said Elrohir. 'But let us speak  no more of 
