line 39000=>     'The  Dead are following,'  said Legolas. 'I  see shapes  of Men and of 
line 39001=>horses,  and  pale  banners  like   shreds   of   cloud,  and   spears  like 
line 39002=>winter -thickets on a misty night. The Dead are following.' 
line 39003=>     'Yes, the Dead ride behind. They have been summoned,' said Elladan. 
line 39004=>     The Company  came at last out of the ravine, as suddenly as it they had 
line 39005=>issued  from  a crack in a wall; and there  lay the uplands  of a great vale 
