line 39249=>that road came soon to the black Dimholt under Dwimorberg, and the menace 
line 39250=>of 
line 39251=>the pillar of stone, and the yawning shadow of the forbidden door. 
line 39252=>     Such was the dark Dunharrow, the work of long -forgotten men. Their name 
line 39253=>was lost and no song or legend remembered it. For what purpose they had 
line 39254=>made 
