line 40342=>     The Gate was shut. All night watchmen on the  walls heard the rumour of 
line 40343=>the enemy that roamed outside,  burning field  and tree, and  hewing any man 
line 40344=>that they found abroad, living or  dead. The numbers that had already passed  
