line 40361=>     At  first  men laughed and did   not greatly fear  such devices. For the 
line 40362=>main  wall of  the City was of great height and  marvellous thickness, built 
line 40363=>ere the power and craft of NÂ®menor waned in exile; and its outward  face was 
