line 40453=>     Far behind the  battle the  River had been swiftly bridged, and all day 
line 40454=>more  force  and  gear of  war had poured across. Now at last  in the middle 
line 40455=>night  the  assault was loosed. The vanguard  passed through the trenches of 
line 40456=>fire by many devious paths that had been  left between  them. On  they came, 
