line 40461=>that the valour of the City was already beaten down, the  hidden Captain put 
line 40462=>forth his strength. Slowly the great siege-towers  built in Osgiliath rolled 
line 40463=>forward through the dark. 
line 40464=>     Messengers came again to the chamber in the White Tower, and Pippin let 
line 40465=>them enter,  for  they were  urgent. Denethor  turned  his head slowly  from 
