line 41009=>Rohan  in that  hour was like a  storm  upon the plain and  a thunder in the 
line 41010=>mountains.  
line 41011=>     Ride now, ride now! Ride to Gondor! 
line 41012=>     Suddenly the king cried to Snowmane and the  horse sprang away.  Behind 
line 41013=>him his banner  blew in the wind,  white horse upon a field of green, but he 
line 41014=>outpaced it. After  him thundered the knights of his house,  but he was ever  
