line 41391=>count. And the  stars flamed in the  sunlight, for they were wrought of gems 
line 41392=>by Arwen daughter of Elrond; and the crown was bright in the morning, for it 
line 41393=>was wrought of mithril and gold. 
line 41394=>     Thus came Aragorn son of Arathorn, Elessar, Isildur's heir, out  of the 
