line 41434=>over; and not one living foe was left within  the circuit of the Rammas. All 
line 41435=>were slain  save those who fled  to die, or to drown  in the red foam of the 
line 41436=>River. Few ever came  eastward to Morgul or Mordor; and  to the land of  the 
line 41437=>Haradrim came only a tale from far off: a rumour of  the wrath and terror of 
