line 42531=>was like the echo of  some forgotten battle in the Dark Years long ago. Pale  
line 42532=>swords were drawn; but I know not whether their blades would still bite, for  
line 42533=>the Dead needed no longer any weapon but fear. None would withstand them. 
line 42534=>     'To every  ship they came that was drawn up, and then  they passed over  
