line 43156=>     Little  time was left to Aragorn for the ordering  of  his battle. Upon 
line 43157=>the one hill he  stood with Gandalf, and there fair and desperate was raised 
line 43158=>the  ba nner of  the  Tree and  Stars.  Upon the other hill hard by stood the 
