line 43254=>time  was. Somewhere between one day and the next, he supposed;  but even of 
line 43255=>the days he had  quite lost count. He  was in a  land  of darkness where the 
line 43256=>days of the world seemed forgotten, and where all who entered were forgotten 
line 43257=>too. 
line 43258=>     'I wonder if they  think of us at all,' he said, 'and what is happening 
