line 44259=>     'Orc-gear's no  good,' said Sam, waving his  arms. 'I  wish I'd  got  an 
line 44260=>orc's hide!' 
line 44261=>     At  last Frodo  could  go  no further.  They had  climbed  up  a narrow 
line 44262=>shelving ravine, but  they still had a long way to go before they could even 
