line 45337=>of the Nazgyl  the shadows of death fell dark upon the earth. Aragorn  stood 
line 45338=>beneath his  banner,  silent and stern, as one lost in thought of things long 
line 45339=>past or far away; but his eyes gleamed like stars that shine the brighter as 
