line 46292=>and 
line 46293=>the power  of the Three Rings also is ended. And all the lands that you see, 
line 46294=>and those that lie round about them, shall be dwellings of Men. For the time 
line 46295=>comes of the Dominion of Men, and the Elder Kindred shall fade or depart.' 
line 46296=>     'I  know it well, dear  friend,' said Aragorn; 'but I would still  have 
line 46297=>your counsel.' 
line 46298=>     'Not for long now,' said Gandalf. 'The Third Age  was my age. I was the 
line 46299=>Enemy of Sauron; and my work  is finished. I shall go soon. The  burden must  
