line 46905=>had  a feeling  that  it  was time he went back to the Shire. Sam shared it. 
line 46906=>Only the night before he had said: 
line 46907=>
line 46908=>####-     'Well, Mr. Frodo, we've been far and seen a deal, and yet I don't think  
