line 47082=>Indeed  most rooms  are empty  these  days, as I'll  not  hide from you, for  
line 47083=>you'll find it out soon enough. And I'll see what can be done  about supper, 
line 47084=>as soon as may be; but I'm short-handed at  present. Hey, Nob you slowcoach!  
