line 47854=>     'To Waymeet, that'll be, ' said  Cotton,  'to fetch  more  of  the gang. 
line 47855=>Well, it's fifteen mile each way. We needn't trouble about them just yet.' 
line 47856=>     Merry  hurried off to  give orders. Farmer Cotton cleared  the  street, 
