line 47968=>burn, and ruin; and now it s come to killing. There s  no longer even any bad 
line 47969=>sense in it. They cut down trees and let 'em lie, they burn houses and build 
line 47970=>no more. 
line 47971=>     'Take Sandyman's mill now. Pimple  knocked it down almost as soon as he 
