line 48546=>What we did in the War of the Ring. 
line 48547=>     Here Bilbo's hand ended and Frodo had written: 
line 48548=> 
line 48549=>     THE DOWNFALL 
line 48550=>     OF THE 
line 48551=>     LORD OF THE RINGS 
line 48552=>     AND THE 
line 48553=>     RETURN OF THE KING 
