line 48588=>     A! Elbereth Gilthoniel! 
line 48589=>     silivren penna mnriel 
line 48590=>     o menel aglar elenath, 
line 48591=>     Gilthoniel, A! Elbereth! 
line 48592=>     We still remember, we who dwell 
line 48593=>     In this far land beneath the trees 
line 48594=>
line 48595=>####-     The starlight on the Western Seas. 
line 48596=>     Frodo and Sam halted and sat silent in the soft shadows, until they saw 
line 48597=>a shimmer as the travellers came towards them. 
line 48598=>     There was Gildor  and  many fair Elven folk; and there  to Sam's wonder  
line 48599=>rode Elrond and Galadriel. Elrond wore a  mantle of grey and had a star upon 
line 48600=>his forehead, and  a silver harp was in his  hand, and upon his finger was a  
line 48601=>ring of gold with a  great blue stone, Vilya, mightiest of  the  Three.  But 
